{
  "stem": "2718.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know-- I don't know if we were one of those people who didn't see the light in time or the so-called the writing on the wall in time.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we lived up to the last minute, almost, like, no, there wouldn't be any danger around, and there wouldn't-- it could never happen, what happened.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] was taken right-- in what-- what [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I will-- ?] if we can start with 1942-- after 1942, they established the labor camp-- not the labor camps.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so it wasn't a labor camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Jews were not allowed anywhere in the army, but they were part of the army.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But instead of-- instead of the regular-- the regular guns or-- or duties the army has, they were-- they were put into separate units.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They-- they worked on the-- on the road construction on whatever that was necessary.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they were more or less the shovel brigade.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- but in the beginning, which was, I think, '42, '43, especially 1942, it was a very, very pleasant way of spending time in the army.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, it was preferred to be a shovel brigade than-- than the army itself because there was no danger.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Nobody went anywhere.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were-- it was in a 100-kilometer radius from the home town.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was no unpleasantness about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, at one stage, we-- my father was in-- was in the army for about a year and one-half.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Came out of these labor armies.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And for a summer holiday, we joined him in the village where he was stationed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we were living at the village.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We just happened to be-- we had relatives in the village.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He was in the camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
